::Aerotaur::
       "Er, I'd love to help sir, but I've got to watch their baby for the 
time being.  I just wouldn't feel right leaving it here alone.  I'm sure 
there are others in the base who can find them."  He sighs and closes the 
comlink to walk over to baby Elita.  "I think you're mom's in a lot of 
trouble.  But I'm sure she'll be okay."  He picks her up again and rocks her 
in his arms.

--part1_54.d89b2a8.2bb279f3_boundary
